product_name: Timex Ironman 50-Lap Sleek Digital Watch - Women's
long_description: The Timex Ironman 50-Lap Sleek digital watch for women sports an array of Ironman-ready features and a durable design. Design features an easy-to-use, push-button format. Features 50-lap memory recall and chronograph with lap or split option. Countdown timer includes countdown stop and countdown repeat. 3 programmable audible alarms with 5 min. back-up alarm and on/off hourly chime. INDIGLO(R) night-light illuminates the display for easy use at night. Polyurethane strap offers enhanced ventilation and flexibility for a seamless fit. The Timex Ironman 50-Lap Sleek digital watch is water resistant to 100m (330 ft.).
short_description: The Timex Ironman 50-Lap Sleek digital watch for women sports an array of Ironman-ready features and a durable design.
